# **AX-Power 1**

Power supply unit with PoE injector and batteries for uninterrupted power supply. ![](images/_page_0_Picture_5.jpeg)

### Introduction

AX-Power 1 is a power supply unit (injector) PoE (Power over Ethernet) according to the standard IEEE 802.3at, with uninterruptible power as the unit includes 2 pcs. batteries (12V 1.3 Ah).
